.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, airplane, motorbike, boat
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, chestnut, blood-red, yellow
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the person who likes blood-red is between the owner of the dog and the person who likes chestnut##2
 2. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the person driving the skateboard is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person who likes chestnut##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who likes grey is the owner of the frog##1
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person who likes blood-red##8
12. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
13. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
15. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the person driving the skateboard is not to the right of the person who likes chestnut##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Transport      | skateboard | motorbike | boat  | airplane  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Color   | chestnut    | blood-red  | yellow | grey |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | dog    | frog  |

