 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blood-red##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person who likes lavender##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person who likes purple##8
 7. the journalist is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes lavender is not to the left of the freelancer##8
12. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
