.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, skateboard, train
There 4 different types of food: tomato, pepper, spinach, strawberry
There are 4 different nationalities: british, malaysian, polish, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person eating tomato is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
 2. the russian is the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is not the person driving the helicopter##6
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 5. the person eating tomato is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person eating tomato##8
 7. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
 8. the malaysian is the person eating pepper##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
10. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person eating tomato##8
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person driving the train and the person eating pepper##2
12. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the person eating pepper##8
14. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
