The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, scooter, van
 1. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
 2. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person eating carrot##8
 3. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person playing canasta##8
 4. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
 5. the person driving the scooter is the nigerian##1
 6. the person playing go is not to the right of the dutch##8
 7. the person playing chess is not the thai##6
 8. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person playing chess##7
 9. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
10. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
11. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
12. the person eating mango is not the argentine##6
13. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
14. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing go##1
15. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person eating mango##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
