.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, security-guard, doctor, mechanic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
House: colonial, cape-cod, art-deco, craftsman
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the cape-cod house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the colonial house is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
 6. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the doctor##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the cape-cod house is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the colonial house is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the security-guard##8
11. the doctor is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the craftsman house is in an odd position##4
13. the doctor is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
