 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 8. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the german##3
 9. the british is not to the left of the person playing go##8
10. the person eating peach is not the brazilian##6
11. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
12. the italian is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the person playing go##8
14. the brazilian is on the right of the person eating peach##1

