.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, lemon, pineapple, apricot
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, social-worker, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, western
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, cain, bongani, havana
 1. the person eating apricot is not to the left of the bartender##8
 2. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the right of the bongani-smoker##5
 4. the teacher is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person eating pineapple is not the social-worker##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the cain-smoker##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the social-worker##8
 8. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
 9. the bongani-smoker is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person eating pineapple is between the social-worker and the person eating apricot##2
13. the person eating apricot is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Food         | apricot    | pineapple   | tomato   | lemon |
| Job           | bartender | doctor    | social-worker | teacher    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | adventure | animation     | western    |
| Cigar   | baccarat   | bongani      | cain         | havana     |

 